longBusinessSummary: Margaret Lake Diamonds Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral resource properties in Canada. The company holds a 60% interest in the Diagras property that consists of 31 mineral claims comprising an area of 22,595 hectares located in the prolific north-northeastern part of the Lac de Gras kimberlite field in the Northwest Territories, Canada. It also holds interest in the Old Nick Nickel-Cobalt project located in Southern British Columbia; and Letain Nickel-Cobalt project located in North-Western British Columbia. The company was formerly known as JDV Capital Corp. and changed its name to Margaret Lake Diamonds Inc. in March 2014. Margaret Lake Diamonds Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
